{"body": "Thank you @elfassy, but we don't actually merge additions to active support unless they're required / could be useful in the Rails codebase and for the vast majority of users.\r\n\r\nSince this apparently does not pass these conditions, I'm giving it a close. Please feel free to come up with more suggestions on where it could be used and why, and if we get useful ones and more people to approve, we can think about reopening.\r\n\r\nThanks!", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/16115855", "created_at": "2013-04-09T14:32:25Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10141#issuecomment-16115855", "updated_at": "2013-04-09T14:32:25Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 10141, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/carlosantoniodasilva", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F60b997fd68261ce70cadaf6c8226c042.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/received_events", "gravatar_id": "77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "carlosantoniodasilva", "type": "User", "id": 26328, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237e2e7bd3543c15100907d"}, "id": 16115855, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos